      Parameters:
      axisName - A name representing the physical nature of the axis like Spatial, Spectral, Time, Velocity or any other free name for an axis .
      ucd - The physical meaning of the axis, Type: standard semantic tag defined in the UCD list.
      unit - default unit for the axis: Type: controlled unit vocabulary following the VOTable units definitions .
      independentAxis - Indicates wether the axis is independent or not from the other axes. The Observable axis has a false independentAxis 'value' Type : boolean .
      calibrationStatus - defines if and how the axis is calibrated: Possible String values: CALIBRATED, UNCALIBRATED, RELATIVE, NORMALIZED .
      undersamplingStatus - A flag to mention wether the data are undersampled. Type: boolean .
      regularsamplingStatus - A flag to mention wether the data are regularly sampled. Type : boolean .
      coordsystem - Reference coordinate system for the axis: .
      ObsyLoc - Observatory location Type: a STC:observatoryLocationType or an xlink .
      accuracy - Global accuracy description of the axis .
